Hello from Amazon Selling Partner Support,
The answers to your questions about resuming sales are as follows:
We have contacted the relevant team to request an inquiry and have received a response  The documentation provided is not sufficient for reinstatement.
We are still missing:
    Declaration of Conformity;
    Function of the signatory is missing;
    First Name/Surname of the signatory is missing;
    Signature of the responsible person is missing;
The DoC provided is not complete. Please work with your supplier/manufacturer to provide an updated document. If you have more questions regarding the compliance of your products, some guidance is provided in Seller Central:  https://sellercentral-europe.amazon.com/help/hub/reference/GUH6FA4XSJ2LZFLY
    Pictures of the product and/or packaging showing mandatory markings: translated age warnings for the remaining EU MPs where applicable;
    Instructions for use translated into each corresponding language according to the country of sales;
The documents must be submitted in a PDF/ZIP format.
⭐ Reminder ⭐:
